However, it is important to note that the impact of my actions was limited, as the accurate figures regarding the company's emissions were disclosed by another source just five weeks later. While I recognize the harm caused by my involvement in this situation, I truly believe that the subsequent revelation of the true numbers mitigated the consequences of my actions.

